pageContext.title: Black Eyed King Imp - Vietnamese Coffee Edition
pageContext.description: This is the Vietnamese Coffee Edition. At 12.7% ABV, Black Eyed King Imp is a super intense and twistedly complex brew, with intense notes of sweet vanilla, rich espresso, smooth molasses and bitter chocolate barely contained by the whatever container it's in.
pageContext.author: Sam Mason <samjbmason>
